title: NYX Doll Eye Mascara, Extreme Black,  Volume,  DE02, 0.28 oz
description: Hello doll-face! For irresistibly fluttery eyelashes, try this mascara on for size. Doll eye mascara uses a unique blend of natural oils, vitamin E and nylon fibers to extend eyelashes to almost faux proportions. This mascara will add the volume in your lashes that you desire.

title: NYX Eyebrow Cake Powder, Black/Gray
description: Our recipe for cooking up exquisite eyebrows includes wax, tools and a pair of complementary powders, black and gray, which can be customized to create the ideal shade. Each eyebrow cake powder kit includes a slanted brush and a round wand to shape, style and tame eyebrows.

title: e.l.f. Essential Eyelid Primer-7501 Sheer
